Interface JsScope.Declarative

  • All Superinterfaces:
    JsScope
    Enclosing interface:
    JsScope

    public static interface JsScope.Declarative
extends JsScope
    Mirrors declarative scope. It's all scopes except 'with' and 'global'. This scope has a well-defined set of variables.
